```

## Example
```
python3 ATHENApp_plot_tool/plot_slice.py Tests/disk.out2.00800.athdf rho
test_out.png --colormap viridis --vmin 0.0 --vmax 0.2 --x_min=1.0 --x_max=70.0 -dpi 200
```
